title: Dell C730C SoundBar Sound Bar Speakers AX510+AS510PA (Power Adapter Included) for Dell UltraSharp LCD Flat Panel Monitors
description:
Genuine Dell AX510 Soundbar speakers. The Soundbar also includes volume control, two headphone jacks on the sides, and an A/C power adapter. 

These speakers will mount to the following UltraSharp Flat Panel Displays and P Series Flat panel Displays: 
1703FP, 1704FP, 1707FP, 1707FPV, 1708FP,  1801FP,  1901FP, 1905FP, 1907FP, 1907FPV, 1908FP, 1908WFP, 1908WFP, SP1908FP, SE198WFP, 2001FP, 2005FP, 2005FPW, 2007FP, 2007WFP,  2009W, 2208WFP, 2408WFP,  2707WFP, 3007WFP, 3007FPW, 3007WFP-HC, 3008WFP, E152FP, E153FP, E156FP, E157FP, E157FPT, E172FP, E173FP, E176FP, E177FP, E178FP, E178FPW, E193FP, E196FP, E197FP, E198FP, E198WFP, E207WFP, E228WFP, E248WFP, SE177FP, SE178WFP, SE197FP, SE198WFP, S199WFP, SP2208WFP,  P2309W, ST2210, ST2310, ST2410, SX2210T, P190S, U2711.

Compatible Part Numbers: AX510, AX510PA, C730C, DW711, 313-6412, 313-6219, 313-6413, 313-6412.
